# Amnezia Cloak requires zero runtime environment variables.
#
# This file exists only to document that fact for tooling that expects an
# .env.example in every repo. The app reads from:
#   - /etc/amnezia/amneziawg/*.conf   (tunnel configs, root-owned)
#   - /var/run/amneziawg/*.name       (runtime utun pointers)
# and shells out to fixed paths under /usr/local/{bin,sbin}/.
#
# If you're looking for an "install prefix" knob: there isn't one yet. If you
# need it, open a feature request.
